Migwagwa mikuru yakafara, zvivakwa zvine magirazi mberi uyezve nzvimbo dzezvitoro nekutengesa zvakazara nematenga ane mataira matsvuku, musika wezana rechi18, uye pekunamatira pemaMuslim nemachechi, kunyangwe guta racho richiratidzika nekunzwika kunge Mediterranean Europe kupfuura Turkey yechinyakare.
